        <h1>Our Story</h1>
        <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0549/5082/2118/files/story-img1.jpg?v=1632801656" class="story-img-mob forMob">
        <p class="story-txt1">How it started...</p>
        <p class="story-txt2">Our story started with an awakening to the corporate greed in a billion-dollar beauty industry… and a desire to go against it.</p>
        <p class="story-txt2">It’s not hard to see that the beauty industry is corrupt. While there’s no such thing as “perfect”, that’s the last thing the industry wants you to believe. Instead, they showcase 20-year-old photoshopped runway models and create an unattainable and unrealistic image for young women. Why? Because it puts more money in their pockets.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="story-imgdv fr">
        <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0549/5082/2118/files/story-img1.jpg?v=1632801656" class="story-img">
