    </div>
    <div class="story-bndleBx">
      <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0549/5082/2118/files/story-bndle-img.png?v=1632801791" class="story-bndle-img">
      <div class="story-bndleBx-rght">
        <p class="story-txt2">But more importantly, it makes it almost impossible for women of all ages to feel comfortable in their own bodies.</p>
        <p class="story-txt2">As women age, it becomes even more complicated. The products you see in retail stores are almost never formulated for women with mature skin. Even if they claim to be “anti-aging”, they’re still designed for younger women who don’t yet show any signs of aging. We know first-hand, what works for a woman in her 20s or 30s is NOT going to work for a woman in her 50s, 60s, and beyond.</p>
        <p class="story-txt2">This is why we created Fièra Cosmetics… for women of 40 who are fed up with watching their cabinets fill up with overpriced products that simply don’t work for their skin. For women who don’t just want to prevent future signs of aging, but actually reduce the signs of aging that are already visible, and improve their skin over time. </p>
        <p class="story-txt2">&nbsp;</p>
      </div>
