        <p class="story-txt1">How it’s going…</p>
        <p class="story-txt2">We are proud to say that not only have we truly delivered on our promises to help hundreds of thousands of mature women improve the look and health of their skin with our products… but our customers have helped fuel our mission. </p>
        <p class="story-txt2">We’re committed to celebrating the beauty of aging, and showing the world that women over 40 deserve to be fairly served by and represented in the beauty industry.</p>
