        <p class="story-txt1">Fièra continues to go against the greed in this industry, praying on insecurities with false promises and overpriced products that don’t work.</p>
        <p class="story-txt2">That’s why we use real women ages 40 and above in our advertising. We use actual customers with real testimonials, and mature women who have seen first-hand just how effective our products really are. This representation gives women realistic expectations of the results they can achieve using our products.</p>
        <p class="story-txt2">Our ecommerce model means that don’t pay retail giants for shelf space where the prime spots go to the highest bidder. We’ve cut out the middle-man and put that money where it matters… into scientifically-proven ingredients that help women regain their skin's long-term health and beauty.</p>
        <p class="story-txt2">We’re incredibly proud to have a growing group of customers, ambassadors and models who feel empowered to look and feel their best at every age, and who are inspiring others to do the same.</p>
